
Pre-requisites

Requires the use of the LÖVE repo. Enable ppa (without actually installing LÖVE) with the following prior to using snapcraft

  sudo add-apt-repository ppa:bartbes/love-stable
  sudo apt-get update -qq

Building

SNAPCRAFT_LOCAL_SOURCES=1 snapcraft snap

Issues

Currently broken due to libGL issue https://trello.com/c/Rwt1nitw/12-libgl-access-in-snaps
